Packages 
Package Description
classifier Classifier package that provides a generic interface. It allows to estimate a model by offering a fit method wich needs training data and its classification. It also allows to predict data using the model obtained with the fit method.
graph This package has a Graph class wich uses a generic Node that can store any generic data type. It also provides a NodeInfo class which can be used has Node data to store usefull information.
main Contains the main method.
metrics Provides generic metrics interface and several metrics implementation such as, F1 score, accuracy, specificty, sensitivity and confusion matrix.
score Provides a score interface that calculates a weight. It contains LL and MDL score implementation.
spanningTree Provides a generic spanningTree interface and a Kruskal's algorithm implementation.
tree Provides a class to calculate Naive Bayes Classifier parameters.
